</oo>

<p>Solid red circle in Fig. <a href="#fig:fig:vsf-boxchar">1</a> means that $f_{\rm BC}$ has value of $A$ at that position, while empty or white circle means that $f _{\rm BC}$ does not have value of $A$.</p>

